channel.title: Can someone please answer my question?
channel.description:
Howdy, How are you all doing? My question is how come when when I tried to run the script (Bumfughter pro 1.1 made by Bumis) I got this code "[Error] (56:51): Duplicate identifier 'UpChars' in script C:\Program Files\SCAR 3.15\includes\ssi2.txt" I'm pretty sure i've downloaded all the included and I have read through tutorials but have yet to find the answer. Thank You ahead of time for whoever answers my question. Cheers
PS. Sorry for any spelling/grammer mistakes... not my best subject :D

item.title: Can someone please answer my question?
item.dc:creator: @Nashi Nashi
item.description:
@Nashi wrote:

Unfortunately that script is very outdated and as you can tell is no longer compatible with the current SCAR.
Also that include is very outdated and I don’t know how you got it unless you got it straight off Freddy’s archive

You should get SRL, It’s the most up to date and current include for SCAR scripts & Scripters.
Also look for some more up to date Scripts, one’s for the current SRL Revision
